{"tid":742711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［人性台］覺唔覺搵人棟係廁所好侮辱","createTime":"2018-07-14T19:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T00:28:45.000Z","uid":82224,"like":90,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3ff0aa65aa1ac2f48d5b83d7626d91b7ead811","tid":742711,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:15:19.000Z","msg":"其實一直以來覺得係商場搵人守住個廁所，啲清潔呀叔棟係到究竟諗緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廁所環境極度惡劣，屎尿味唔在講，其實透啖氣都覺得食左少少屎咁滯<br />\n點解一個人要係咁既工作環境做野？<br />\n將心比己個呀叔都係人啫。清潔係要人做，但無需要時時刻刻都係廁所掛<br />\n要人長期聞臭屎，睇住麻甩佬痾尿個猥瑣樣，聽埋啲嗚呀既放屎屁聲，五種觀感都佔左眼耳鼻三觀既極度污染，簡直係對人類最大侮辱既工作⋯"},{"pid":"0ed49bffdabd02192f8d22ea01e980be680a1f5f","tid":742711,"uid":189053,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c6d2ca0204c6c834d785e034f5a862c17320cb4","tid":742711,"uid":30377,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c159e1b274d2cc83847ae0924646f83b24d1d9ae","tid":742711,"uid":67329,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"3c6d2ca0204c6c834d785e034f5a862c17320cb4","tid":742711,"uid":30377,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:28:32.000Z","msg":"同情一個人守喺廁所度 同 佢靠份工養家有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我未跟到你條思路"},{"pid":"6004659656f5773850a97aa9bc4cad11b58adce4","tid":742711,"uid":2566,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:31:42.000Z","msg":"我都覺得無需要固定一個人長時期守係廁所。"},{"pid":"6d5d7cc0cc585f7a7ef56e5667854638b5dac14f","tid":742711,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:34:48.000Z","msg":"管理公司戇鳩"},{"pid":"79394b685c923fc73ad3a94531e0333f42413000","tid":742711,"uid":82224,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"3c6d2ca0204c6c834d785e034f5a862c17320cb4","tid":742711,"uid":30377,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:35:25.000Z","msg":"係同理心，係人性既挑戰。可能佢地智慧唔夠高，係依個石屎森林搵唔到一種比較好既生存方法，但其他人呢 稍有智慧同理心既人都或者想改善下佢地既工作環境掛。起碼唔駛叫人長期棟係廁所，每4小時一次關閉式清潔可能已經對佢地黎講係一種進步"},{"pid":"bdb88d062c36b3267d7e7b1cf70c9a89744f853f","tid":742711,"uid":92857,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:41:48.000Z","msg":"有d冷係高級既商場會要個姐姐同每個出入既人打招呼<br />\n真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1397bfbbf8f8884e937ad3474abfa9d9945f4b4","tid":742711,"uid":98273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb88d062c36b3267d7e7b1cf70c9a89744f853f","tid":742711,"uid":92857,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:41:48.000Z","msg":"有d冷係高級既商場會要個姐姐同每個出入既人打招呼<br />\n真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:53:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/99315/%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%B7%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%A4%AA%E6%9C%89%E7%A6%AE%E8%B2%8C-%E8%8D%B7%E9%87%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4-%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8-%E5%BE%9E%E6%9C%AA%E8%A9%A6%E9%81%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F99315%2F%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%259C%