sg":"可以自由選擇嘅工作唔存在侮辱<br />\n<br />\n有工作係聞屎，你可以唔做"},{"pid":"485c74c4ad165b248d0e78b501911bec609fe9f7","tid":742711,"uid":17675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T21:22:22.000Z","msg":"唔係對做嗰個侮辱 <br />\n係侮辱用嗰個 同埋對香港/大陸閪 一個認知文化 就係你哋唔撚識用廁所"},{"pid":"8469c3548b3357858e2cc48692af162ab1508830","tid":742711,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T21:24:46.000Z","msg":"冇錢就仆街架啦<br />\n有好心既咪屙尿屙好啲"},{"pid":"af20a28e647e6da88cd2816e96eb205e2d2d14e4","tid":742711,"uid":82224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f4633b2f5b89d67f53116cc1119e36c66b2acc7","tid":742711,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T21:16:44.000Z","msg":"可以自由選擇嘅工作唔存在侮辱<br />\n<br />\n有工作係聞屎，你可以唔做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T23:24:38.000Z","msg":"貌似有選擇，其實邊度有哎"},{"pid":"605af744c71ac3d47b4b6d9972c4fe5f4250c5d8","tid":742711,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T23:37:31.000Z","msg":"但廁所阿叔係唯一工種可以靠自己如改變工作環境既職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5bf5fb130d6eac44548b6b100bcab810355a856","tid":742711,"uid":157841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T23:47:36.000Z","msg":"仲未計塞廁所，屙到週圍都係屎尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3117538c12542b59abc847177e5469d895471c","tid":742711,"uid":84104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T23:58:54.000Z","msg":"見過有啲八婆入到去，可能上一手用得好衰<br />\n即刻喝個姐姐過黎幫佢清潔<br />\n雖然確實係佢負責嘅工作<br />\n但見到都係覺得好心嗡<br />\n要怪就怪個使用者唔自律<br />\n入過香港嘅女廁你先知咩叫核突<br />\n一地尿唔在講，經常整到d邊邊地下都係M血<br />\n有啲痴線到原塊滿血M巾痴係牆上面！"},{"pid":"b6e22b4594080b3dddb94afeaba3c5419c96aaf9","tid":742711,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b3117538c12542b59abc847177e5469d895471c","tid":742711,"uid":84104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep